    slug: "more-than-1000-sunnah-every-day-night-ps",
    description: `More than 1,000 Sunnah every Day and Night (PS) is the pocket-size edition of this comprehensive Urdu-language reference that catalogues over one thousand authentic Sunnah practices of Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) organised according to the daily routine of a Muslim. The PS (pocket-size) designation indicates that this edition has been produced in a smaller, more portable format that can be easily carried in a pocket, handbag, or backpack, making it a convenient daily companion that can be consulted wherever the reader happens to be. Despite its compact dimensions, this pocket edition retains the complete content of the standard edition, covering the full range of Sunnah practices from the moment of waking in the morning through all the daily activities until returning to sleep at night. The book systematically presents each Sunnah practice with its relevant hadith reference and a clear, concise explanation of how to implement it, covering topics such as the supplications upon waking, the etiquette of using the toilet and performing wudu, the morning and evening adhkar, the du'as for eating, drinking, dressing, travelling, entering and leaving the home, the Sunnah practices associated with each of the five daily prayers, the recommended dhikr and du'as for various situations throughout the day, the etiquettes of social interaction, and the supplications and practices recommended before sleeping. The compact format makes this edition particularly useful for students, professionals, and travellers who wish to maintain a conscious practice of following the Sunnah throughout their busy days but cannot carry a large reference book with them. Readers can easily pull the book out during a break at work, between classes, while commuting, or at any spare moment to review the Sunnah practices they should be implementing at that time of day. The smaller page size does not compromise readability, as the text has been formatted with appropriate font sizing and clear spacing to ensure comfortable reading despite the reduced dimensions. The binding is sturdy enough to withstand regular handling and the wear and tear of being carried daily in a pocket or bag. This pocket-size edition also makes an excellent gift, particularly for young people, new Muslims, and anyone who is beginning their journey of learning about and implementing the Sunnah in their daily lives. The convenience of having over a thousand Sunnah practices organised chronologically in a portable format means that readers are more likely to actually use the book consistently, gradually transforming their daily habits to align more closely with the beautiful example of Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) and earning the abundant rewards that Allah has promised for those who follow the Sunnah of His Messenger.`,
